    "source": {
      "goCharacterKey": "RaidenShogun",
      "note": "Normal/charged/plunging generated from Genshin Optimizer sheets (master) + allStat_gen skillParam. skill.dmg/coorDmg and burst.* parsed by hand from libs/gi/sheets/src/Characters/RaidenShogun/index.tsx (2026-07 fix for the previously-unparsed resolve-scaled burst). burst.dmg/hit1-5/charged1-2/plunge/plungeLow/plungeHigh are Musou no Hitotachi + Musou Isshin-infused NA/CA/Plunge; each pre-bakes the 'Resolve' DMG% bonus (Chakra Desiderata) at its max of 60 stacks: burst.dmg uses skillParam.burst[9][1]*60 (resolveBonus1, 'Musou no Hitotachi DMG Bonus Scaling'), the other 11 hits use skillParam.burst[9][2]*60 (resolveBonus2, 'Musou Isshin DMG Bonus Scaling'). Max Resolve is chosen unconditionally because reaching it only requires ~30 elemental particle/orb pickups (2 stacks each, one proc/3s) over a rotation, standard for optimal-play leaderboard modeling. Hit keys match GO target paths; multKey = <hitKey>_mult. Levels: Lv10, C0.",
